OL,3,CWhy has this vegan restaurant been
OL,4,Cforced to start serving meat?
OL,6,FVideo Report by Granada Reports
OL,7,FJournalist Jennifer Buck.
OL,9,FA vegan restaurant in says it has
OL,10,Ftaken the "difficult yet necessary"
OL,11,Fdecision to start serving meat, in
OL,12,Forder to survive.
OL,14,FNomas Gastrobar announced the decision
OL,15,Fon social media saying that in light
OL,16,Fof the "profound" challenges the
OL,17,Fbusiness had faced they would begin
OL,18,Fserving "high quality" and
OL,19,F"responsibly sourced" meat and dairy.
