OL,3,CWhy has this vegan restaurant been
OL,4,Cforced to start serving meat?
OL,6,FThe restaurant, formerly known as
OL,7,FEthos, on Chestergate, was created by
OL,8,FAdonis Norouznia and his wife three
OL,9,Fyears ago after they moved from Greece
OL,10,Fin 2018.
OL,12,FMr Norouznia says as well as the
OL,13,Fincrease in energy prices, they are
OL,14,Falso battling an increase in the cost
OL,15,Fof basic ingredients including plant
OL,16,Fbased milk, bags of flour and cooking
OL,17,Foil.
