OL,3,CWhy has this vegan restaurant been
OL,4,Cforced to start serving meat?
OL,6,FMr Norouznia says that they lose
OL,7,Fcustomers from "several tables" every
OL,8,Fday when they look at the menu and see
OL,9,Fno meat is listed.
OL,11,F"When someone who loves to eat meat
OL,12,Fcomes in and they find there is
OL,13,Fnothing for them to eat then they
OL,14,Fdon't want to eat anything, they do
OL,15,Fnot feel happy to sit, so they leave
OL,16,Fso we are losing customers a lot,
OL,17,Fevery day at least one to two tables a
OL,18,Fday," he said.
