OL,3,CWhy has this vegan restaurant been
OL,4,Cforced to start serving meat?
OL,6,FHe admits though that it a difficult
OL,7,Fdecision to extend the menu to offer
OL,8,Fsome dairy products and meat options.
OL,10,F"Personally I am going to struggle the
OL,11,Fmost in here because I can't stand the
OL,12,Fsmell of meat so it is going to be
OL,13,Fdifficult for me but I have to feed a
OL,14,Ffamily of three kids and I have to pay
OL,15,Fthe wages of the staff," added Mr
OL,16,FNorouznia.
