OL,3,CWhy has this vegan restaurant been
OL,4,Cforced to start serving meat?
OL,6,F"I have to decide, either keep it like
OL,7,Fthis and you will probably hear
OL,8,Fanother vegan restaurant has closed
OL,9,Fdown or adapt to what the market needs
OL,10,Fto be able to survive and yes to make
OL,11,Fmoney."
OL,13,FThe competition is fierce on most high
OL,14,Fstreets, but in Macclesfield there are
OL,15,Fnine cafe's on the stretch of road
OL,16,Falongside Nomas.
