OL,3,CWhy has this vegan restaurant been
OL,4,Cforced to start serving meat?
OL,6,FMr Norouznia said they have already
OL,7,Fexpanded the menu to compete, adding
OL,8,Fpizzas and lunchtime deals but now
OL,9,Fthey have no choice but to offer a
OL,10,Fwider menu.
OL,12,FMost of the lunchtime customers
OL,13,Funderstood the move, one saying: "It
OL,14,Fmeans you can come in with a friend
OL,15,Fwho isn't vegan and there is more
OL,16,Fchoice."
OL,18,FWhile another said: "It seems a bit
OL,19,Fsad that it was all vegan and that
OL,20,Fhasn't work for them."
